HEADWORD: Cadrans
<hw>Cad"rans</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>cadran</ets>. Cf. <er>Quadrant</er>.]</ety> <def>An instrument with
